column5: i am heading to Tobin lake Sask. at the end of sept.for trophy walleye..Has anyone benn there lately to give me a report on how the fishing is and where and what they are biting on? Also i had a guy tell me that there is smallies in this lake, is this true??? Thanks!
Hey Jeff go to www.gowalleye.com and check out the message board.There someone will answer your questions.FISH ON.
